column5: The rain was threatening but holding off while I was there hopefully it stayed away until after 9pm, Money raised to help with the Hatchery Program Tight Lines SBK  Fish Fry Video
wow that looks so good!! Great efforts out there Richard
Nice documentation Richard ..you are an asset to the Club!   good on ya !!

Sounds like they had 340 People at the Fish Fry & they cooked 100 lbs of Whitefish, 120 lbs of Walleye and about 100 lbs of donated Trout and Salmon, making over $1,500.00. Hats Off to Al & all the rest of the Volunteers Tight Lines SBK
